      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "title": "Unrivaled Fit",
        "subtitle": "<p>Unlike generic brands that merely scale up sizes, Strongsize is solely dedicated to the big and tall community. Our approach is different: we functionally engineer our clothing from scratch, exclusively for big and tall body types. <strong>Explore our </strong><a href=\"https://strongsize.com/collections/big-and-tall-crewneck-tshirts\"><strong>Crewneck T-Shirts</strong></a><strong>, </strong><a href=\"https://strongsize.com/collections/xl-8xl-big-tall-polo-shirts\"><strong>XL–8XL Polo Shirts</strong></a><strong>, and </strong><a href=\"https://strongsize.com/collections/big-tall-shirt-bundles\"><strong>Shirt Bundles</strong></a><strong> crafted exclusively for big & tall men.</strong><br/><br/></p>",
        "link_text": "Learn More",
        "link_url": "shopify://pages/fit-guide"
      }
    },
    "wd2_video_9dXQjj": {
      "type": "wd2-video",
      "blocks": {
        "video_ECkP8D": {
          "type": "video",
          "settings": {
            "video": "shopify://files/videos/Strongsize 2025_Us v Them_Final_No GFX (1).mp4"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "video_ECkP8D"
      ],
      "name": "WD2 Video",
      "settings": {
        "title": "Big and Tall Clothing That Actually Fits.",
        "subtitle": "<p>Most brands add a 2XL and call it inclusive. We call that an afterthought. Strongsize <a href=\"/collections/t-shirts\" title=\"T-Shirts\">t-shirts</a> and <a href=\"/collections/polos\" title=\"Polos\">polos</a> are size-exclusive, engineered from XL to 8XL for big men and no one else.</p>",
        "link_text": "VIEW ALL TOPS",
        "link_url": "shopify://collections/big-and-tall-tops"
      }
    },
    "wd_testimonials_KFf6yT": {
      "type": "wd-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_Ng3wMF": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": false,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Chase F.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>I'm a big dude and this is by far the best fitting shirt I've ordered in a long time. I liked it so much the first time, I ordered 2 more for work. Breathable, long enough to cover my bum when I bend over, material is semi stretchy in all directions, and wicks sweat away pretty well.</p><p>(6’2”, 365 lbs, 5XL Longer)</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_bQfgQx": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Cameron C.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>The fit of this tee is amazing. I like the longer length as it helps prevent showing my underwear when I’m bending over or lifting my arms. The quality of the fabric is excellent, nice stretch, cool, and little to no shrinking after wash. After this arrived and I tried it on, I immediately bought 3 more.</p><p>(6’0”, 215 lbs, XL Longer)</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_gXYfDC": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Leo B.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>I’ve tried dozens of brands and wasted tons of money trying to find a fit that suited my build. Wish I would have found out about Strongsize years ago. Larger sizes in most brands have huge arms and chest, this brand fits nice in those areas without being huge. I’ll likely never try another brand again, it fits that nice and feels that good!</p><p>(6'1”, 390 lbs, 4XL Longer)</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_hgYNxh": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Amanda P.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>Got this for my husband and he says the shirt fits amazing and feels great. I have to agree, I've never seen him look so good in a tee before! He loves it so much we are ordering more. Really great bang for your buck.</p><p>(5’9”, 400 lbs, 5XL Regular)</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "testimonial_Ng3wMF",
        "testimonial_bQfgQx",
        "testimonial_gXYfDC",
        "testimonial_hgYNxh"
      ],
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
